715
00:26:23,748 --> 00:26:25,216
-You're right.
-Don't tease him.

716
00:26:25,283 --> 00:26:26,651
Stop teasing his baldness.

717
00:26:26,718 --> 00:26:27,986
He's not bald.

718
00:26:28,053 --> 00:26:29,621
-He's not?
-No.

719
00:26:29,888 --> 00:26:31,456
THE THICK-HAIRED EAGLE

720
00:26:31,523 --> 00:26:34,392
