728
00:26:49,341 --> 00:26:51,242
He's the one

729
00:26:51,309 --> 00:26:54,813
-who always shares my updates.
-That's true.

730
00:26:54,879 --> 00:26:56,615
-He always does that.
-He does.

731
00:26:56,681 --> 00:26:58,683
You never said anything,

732
00:26:58,750 --> 00:27:01,786
but Ho-young always shares your updates.

733
00:27:01,853 --> 00:27:04,923
Chef Ho-young, why do you
take advantage of Kang-rok?

734
00:27:04,990 --> 00:27:06,992
When I upload his picture
on my social media,

735
00:27:07,058 --> 00:27:09,628
-I suddenly gain many more followers.
-I see.

736
00:27:09,694 --> 00:27:11,262
