something very unsightly.

739
00:27:15,967 --> 00:27:18,303
-I saw that too.
-What is it?

740
00:27:18,370 --> 00:27:20,305
What's the news on Ho-young?

741
00:27:20,372 --> 00:27:22,440
-He uploads a lot of pictures.
-I was so surprised.

742
00:27:22,507 --> 00:27:24,776
That day, he probably had
nothing else to post,

743
00:27:24,843 --> 00:27:26,411
so he posted a female version of himself.

744
00:27:26,478 --> 00:27:27,579
IT'S AN AI-GENERATED IMAGE

745
00:27:28,046 --> 00:27:30,115
HYUN-SUK: DON'T JUST DO
EVERYTHING YOU WANT TO DO

746
00:27:30,181 --> 00:27:33,051
Sam, you usually leave a comment.
Did you not leave one there?

747
00:27:33,118 --> 00:27:35,220
I just pressed like and left the app.

748
00:27:35,286 --> 00:27:36,388
HE STILL PRESSED LIKE

749
00:27:36,454 --> 00:27:37,856
-You pressed like?
-I see.

750
00:27:37,922 --> 00:27:39,791
