the female version of yourself?

751
00:27:39,858 --> 00:27:44,195
It's been a while since <i>CCW2</i> had aired,
so it's not as popular at this point.

752
00:27:44,262 --> 00:27:48,633
So I noticed
a clear drop on the number of likes.

753
00:27:48,700 --> 00:27:50,035
-Yes, it's noticeable.
-I thought

754
00:27:50,101 --> 00:27:53,071
-I needed something shocking and new.
-You're right.

755
00:27:53,138 --> 00:27:56,775
So I got lots of likes for that post,
but many said they'd unfollow me.

756
00:27:56,841 --> 00:27:58,910
I thought about it too.

757
00:27:58,977 --> 00:28:00,578
I also

758
00:28:00,645 --> 00:28:02,747
blocked him for a moment,
then unblocked him.

759
00:28:03,048 --> 00:28:04,182
BACKFIRED BADLY

760
00:28:04,249 --> 00:28:08,987
One of them feels troubled
when you give him attention,

761
00:28:09,054 --> 00:28:12,624
but the other feels troubled
when he doesn't get attention.

762
00:28:13,458 --> 00:28:15,527
CHEF KANG-ROK'S INGREDIENTS:
