821
00:30:34,365 --> 00:30:35,533
Kang-rok.

822
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:36,768
Kang-rok.

823
00:30:36,835 --> 00:30:38,703
<i>Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry</i>

824
00:30:38,770 --> 00:30:41,706
<i>Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry</i>

825
00:30:41,773 --> 00:30:42,874
